{"tid":1684760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足入。。。「（和理勇）有重要事商討！！！」長文［慎入］","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:04:10.000Z","uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c57a692cebd0c24898b02a59c4330121d2cdeba8","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"係戰場上，當你手執盾和劍，劍為攻，而盾為守，但係點解我哋用嘅時候唔係並用，而係分開嚟用？<br />\n<br />\n劍和盾嘅特性相反，但係佢哋有一個共通點，就係同為武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我將佢比喻為我哋。相信大家都成日都聽到一句：「勇武為劍，和理非為盾」講嘅就係想講，我哋係一套互相保護、互相配合可以由守轉為攻，亦可以由攻切換為守嘅武器，而真正識得發揮劍盾嘅作用時，就係等於一個識得上戰場嘅士兵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講我哋一直有一個錯誤嘅諗法，就係覺得互相係唔同嘅兩樣嘢，變成咗一套唔會攻但係又會守嘅劍盾武具。<br />\n<br />\n言歸正轉，有關11月2號嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（參考十一國殤）點解我哋呢日可以咁？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 係港島遊行依然進行，記得當日有民陣發起嘅國殤日遊行，但係點解重可以做到六區開花依然夠人？</span></span><br />\n係因為我哋識得點去運用多人嘅優勢，製造出劍盾戰術！！！！分散開花，用人多啲力量去抗衡政府同狗/中國兵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2 . 方法？</span></span><br />\n係遊行進行時或途中再六/七區開花，變相遊行變得可聚更多人，有更多人唔怕出尼，因為佢哋無gear多數和理非，狗告唔到佢哋，佢哋最多48小時，到有包伏、有小朋友嘅家庭去行，而狗一定要幫手睇住個場，變咗分散警力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3 . 開花必須係一啲穩陣地方</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例子：去一啲有遊行/集會去過嘅地方，而開花，就可以為一啲交通不便嘅手足另想地點，同埋可以令手 足唔洗搭車行到返去嘅地方，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">一，沙田</span></span><br />\n（有遊行過，開花打過，沙燕橋之役）可能住沙田/大圍/到馬鞍山嘅手足都熟路，可以周圍捐，又可以唔洗經隧道同過海返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">二，屯元天</span></span><br />\n（識路嘅可能會左穿右插，例，天水圍 = 一個圈，人哋以為好大，可能識路嘅人係屋邨識路走，隨時救到手足，另外，元朗（有遊行過）屯（有試過開花）天水圍（親子遊行）全部都行過，可以減低大欖隧道屯元天手足被check車，唔敢帶 gear，要被迫有勇武但行唔到前，前線要人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">三，將軍澳區</span></span><br />\n（識路人都識行，其實好細，之前試過有遊行，覺得可以一戰）因為佢哋每次去港島、或者係比較安全嘅九龍都好難返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">四，黃大仙可以轉場</span></span><br />\n次次重狗，上次慘敗，咩都未做就比狗車追，有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五，荃葵青</span></span><br />\n（荃灣開花）都係試過，荃灣遊行，為健仔報仇，同埋之前就係第一次用火魔令到狗唔敢行嘅地方，識路嘅人可以返埋青衣。減低難返屋企嘅風險，有好多手足返唔到去就住一晩，最後被伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">六，油尖旺區</span></span><br />\n可以都係住呢區手足嘅主戰場，唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">七，maybe！</span></span><br />\n港島要視乎緊急情況而定，睇狗對我哋點，否則唔好係港島開戰，遊行大隊 = 和理非主場。<br />\n<br />\n之前十一都得嫁，點解要局限咗自己？俗語都有話啦，做人唔可以死板，老闆只會鍾意識轉彎，唔會鍾意一啲叫你衝，而你又衝到沿涯唔停嘅人，人哋識得變通改作戰策略，我哋都得，唔係話咗要一齊反抗嫁咩？遊行同開花可以同時進行，如果我哋淨係識得係一個地方戀戰，當我係狗都開心啦，唔洗做咁多嘢，扔個tg過尼，大圍捕，所以如果係咁，我哋就要識運用我哋唯一嘅優勢，就係人多！！！！更何況我哋知道對我哋有利嘅打法，知道原來可以咁做嫁喎，咁點解唔好好利用我哋嘅優點？<br />\n<br />\n假設 狗 30000人 + 大陸軍 4000人<br />\n實際得10000真狗 + 4000大陸狗<br />\n佢哋都要放假，同有文職、後勤、冷氣高層，而我哋200萬人喎？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以係輪班際下，我哋開花 + 遊行同時進行，分散警力，有我哋優勢，就可能贏，我哋太執著<br />\n打團戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4 . 打狗救人</span></span><br />\n當狗同手足比例一比五有手足被打，我哋可以長遮，一，二，三，有冇人打波跟隊，有手足就衝同上，其實佢哋重驚過我哋。<br />\n<br />\n4：30 集會上訴申請已被駁回，變通啊，香港人。<br />\n最後<br />\n#光復香港 時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#香港人 反抗 112"},{"pid":"73cc942807625eae80d65cec3cb7abc9d751348d","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"7f23d1092533c636120f5d889022756d33cb28cd","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"50f93898dacd3a86dee0041ee9d63a742589900b","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"5fe1c59203428598cf8414d8462393f63ba295fc","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"969945ef1fc86170c80a5cdc43c21a78e9728d1c","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"bd7b4c69f8b115bbd0aeadfa116e518899f01f30","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"e738527fffb78f1df5aabb3ddec7f72313bb141a","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"becb3aeb477d5c7727620fa6985cd0ecae5282df","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"4ec79a711bdba25cb0bdb07e4aa7257ef756d36d","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"9578556da10dc24cb547f9f1807b8648e241bf7d","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"自推 10/10"},{"pid":"57637d52f5f8c63f57604aa907070677acb2d03d","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"71053a22340dad54e12f47b7ef96d90dd43de35c","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"6991f9726f63aaea6fa861d8f1674d0ea1bc9db7","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33db66a6632161411698b183e7c7a955f02ee794","tid":1684760,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"明明有共識維園又想吹風分散人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d882b640c1acfdcc9062d314aed3a39ee63b48","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:11:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6fc5efa2478db501ffa27d366eacac29ed361ed","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33db66a6632161411698b183e7c7a955f02ee794","tid":1684760,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"明明有共識維園又想吹風分散人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"點解可以唔識變通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當大家都身處過港島嘅恐懼就會明，金鐘開始諗水炮車推緊，銅鑼灣、灣仔又夾緊過嚟，就會諗死啦點算！<br />\n<br />\n重有，我知你想講咩，唔勇武咪得囉，講笑咩，你個遊行集會唔合法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔好自己走到就當無事先得㗎，你走到，手足走唔到啊，人哋幫你頂完，比人塔咗返去，你就當人condom？咪玩啦<br />\n<br />\n重有！<br />\n次次都係狗打鳩我哋先，有咩計，人哋上次10月27和理非照拉啦，唔好講到咁之前，你話琴日，有手足比人入埋樓，係大堂搜啊，看鋪嘅老闆娘都被捕，講真，重要天真到幾時？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次都港島1800米大直路，你咁只係益咗班狗一個tg夾推，手足被捕，就係要開化先係我哋優勢，唔好再咁執著港島啦，你走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋走唔到啊！<br />\n<br />\n得三條隧道又封鐡，新界人？九西人？將軍澳西貢人？佢哋點？唔好咁自私啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想打就係要咁，劍盾合一，同時並用。"},{"pid":"8e2782564c89e6e785e938b7719dcae478428a54","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2ff8e336e11af00029d0f4330f9a01a0efb904b","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:31:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0e5197167d35cd4675d9d9a36a5dd7d04728563","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"我明白太急，但係我唔想再有手足有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bd5c87754a2b7c735b4e0d6a4aec0af391475d","tid":1684760,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"77d605471c837ec363641311d74f373b3ce744d3","tid":1684760,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0c45Ea1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0c45Ea1.jpg&h=79afa639&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}